{
  "stem": "15938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was a-- there wasn't an official judge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If there was some trouble between people, he was always called in to-- and I don't know if you know what the word 'guber' means.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're a so-called 'guber,' you know, he was kind of one of the people who got called in to do, to make peace or to judge or to--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, no, they did call them for non-Jewish too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, there wasn't-- there wasn't such a-- there weren't enough people for two sections.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you know, you got called in to judge between two people fighting over two inches of land or the cow wandered off to somebody else's field or, he used to go to help as a judgment in the peace.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We dealt in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how to explain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I say hotel, it sounds very-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had rooms where people used to come and stay.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, as I said before, it was a holiday place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like a hotel today but in a much smaller and much-- and he also dealt with vine and drinks, imported, also a very fancy word.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He used to buy up-- he used to go to Hungary and buy up so many acres of grapes and had them made into wine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we supplied the vine for the town, kosher wine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody came to us to buy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had cellars with barrels and that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was his main occupation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I think he was also a land owner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Quite a lot of the houses belonged to the family, you know, all the Birenbaums and so--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like a biggish bungalow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a very big garden.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
